text: Brigita Partikaitė (born 17 May 1991) is a Lithuanian former footballer who played as a defender. She has been a member of the Lithuania women's national team. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Lithuanian women's footballers Category:Lithuania women's international footballers Category:Gintra Universitetas players
